dBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五大底線<br />\n1. 不打記者 <br />\n2. 不打救護<br />\n3. 不濫用酷刑 <br />\n4. 不攻擊平民<br />\n5.  冷靜，不被帶風向，要獨立思考</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"dc6d10d5a94406e5c3414710e88e0949900cb4f8","tid":1467024,"uid":98826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62eb482b20db33cddc086c3d660c08ac906dcb3e","tid":1467024,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:04.000Z","msg":"三毛好撚嬲個環時被捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:53.000Z","msg":"代表做法正確！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009bb9b9fb22473cca245b8a68a2a11e0860b738","tid":1467024,"uid":203619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:10:30.000Z","msg":"我只推 正常POST<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/RfNfTgW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfNfTgW.png&h=52691539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我今日留意到警察係機場用槍指嚇市民<br />\n你呢?"},{"pid":"3a908ca5af1c6a23b812bd03677f98914d997bc2","tid":1467024,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d41b02fbcfc1b90f2a48c37404116418165d81","tid":1467024,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d088bd2b76340dc63ce6df47daa6a2fb77b12ee","tid":1467024,"uid":84949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Royal-Hong-Kong-Regiment-The-Volunteers-712822242120609/?hc_location=ufi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRoyal-Hong-Kong-Regiment-The-Volunteers-712822242120609%2F%3Fhc_location%3Dufi&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ij5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=e524ff3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Royal-Hong-Kong-Regiment-The-Volunteers-712822242120609/?hc_location=ufi</a><br />\n兩軍交戰有基本守則，如果偽裝成對方人員，被捕後可即場槍決 !<br />\n<br />\n1944年12月16日，盟軍登陸諾曼第後向德國逐步進逼，希特拉將所有兵力集中在比利時亞登地區，孤注一擲發動絕地反擊，展開突出部之役(Battle of Bulge)，並且派出由奧托.史科尼兹率領的一支受過特別訓練，並且能講流利美式英語的約160人特種部隊，穿上由戰俘身上獲得的美軍制服，裝備，武器及車輛，假扮成美軍，進行麒麟作戰(Operation Greif)。<br />\n<br />\n德軍特種部隊滲透到美軍後方，更改路標，制做混亂，誤導及趁機殺害毫無防範之小單位美軍。又佔據繆斯河上之橋樑，以保障德軍進攻通道暢通無阻，其後德軍反攻被盟軍瓦解，部隊遭到重創，損失約10萬兵員。<br />\n<br />\n而被捕德軍特種部隊成員由於身穿美軍軍服，故不受日內瓦國際公約(Geneva Conventions)保護，兼且觸犯戰爭罪行，被美軍指揮官命令憲兵即場執行槍決。"},{"pid":"481d53c40e6da55eeed68c470065ffb0d5929d2f","tid":1467024,"uid":117430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:28.000Z","msg":"少少事就引曬班分化撚出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4e55fc1ee0ba09bad414e9cca5f7515824f5a2","tid":1467024,"uid":52574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:58.000Z","msg":"從來都唔係【癱唔癱】既問題，而係【如何癱】既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n求大家睇下同投個票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚係轉捩點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9036dbab0d45917a86aeb7d2e2dea5f0b7311f1","tid":1467024,"uid":98826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"481d53c40e6da55eeed68c470065ffb0d5929d2f","tid":1467024,"uid":117430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:28.000Z","msg":"少少事就引曬班分化撚出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"